front.title: •Scum And Villainy
front.gametext: Deploy on Audience Chamber. While all your ability on table is provided by aliens and independent starship pilots, your aliens and starships deploy -1 and you retrieve 2 Force whenever you initiate battle. (Immune to Alter if you control at least three Jabba's Palace sites.)
front.lore: A relief in Nal Hutta sandstone. Hand-carved by slaves of the great Hutt artist Dreyba. Commissioned by Jabba to illustrate his vast influence. Titled 'Ne Ganna Dateel Jabba.'
